# Files copied into each new `claude --worktree <name>` checkout.
#
# A worktree starts from tracked content only, so the committed safe-default env
# (.env.development) already travels with it and the stack runs out of the box
# (CLAUDE.md invariant #8 — clone-and-run). List here only the *gitignored*
# personal overrides a session would otherwise lose; they win over the committed
# defaults.
#
# NOT copied (intentionally): /target (Rust build cache — heavy; cargo rebuilds
# from its shared registry) and infra/.terraform (provider plugins — re-fetched
# by `terraform init`). Run `cargo build` / `terraform init` inside a worktree
# when you need to build or plan there.
#
# Nothing here is required today (no engine code yet). Uncomment as local
# overrides come into use.
#.env.local
#.env.development.local
